§ PIO_WPMR_WPKEY_PASSWD

#define PIO_WPMR_WPKEY_PASSWD   (0x50494Fu << 8)

(PIO_WPMR) Writing any other value in this field aborts the write operation of the WPEN bit.

Always reads as 0.
